tting-link-${key}`\">Link</label>\r\n            <input class=\"homey-form-input\" :id=\"`app-setting-name-${key}`\" type=\"text\" v-model=\"appSetting.link\"/>\r\n          </div>\r\n          <div class=\"grid-item\">\r\n            <button class=\"homey-button-danger-shadow\" v-on:click.prevent=\"onDeleteAppClick(key)\">Delete</button>\r\n          </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <button class=\"homey-button-secondary-shadow\" v-on:click.prevent=\"onAddAppClick\">Add app</button>\r\n      </fieldset>\r\n    </form>\r\n  </div>\r\n</template>\r\n<script>\r\nimport { mapActions, mapState } from 'pinia'\r\nimport { useWindowStore } from '@/stores/window'\r\n\r\nexport default {\r\n  name: 'AndroidTVAppSettings',\r\n  data () {\r\n    return {}\r\n  },\r\n  computed: {\r\n    // gives read access to this.count and this.double\r\n    ...mapState(useWindowStore, ['apps', 'locales']),\r\n    hasApps () {\r\n      return this.app && this.apps.length && this.apps.length > 0\r\n    }\r\n  },\r\n  methods: {\r\n    ...mapActions(useWindowStore, ['addApp', 'deleteApp']),\r\n    onAddAppClick () {\r\n      this.addApp({ name: '', link: '' })\r\n    },\r\n    onDeleteAppClick (key) {\r\n      this.deleteApp(key)\r\n    }\r\n  }\r\n}\r\n</script>\r\n\r\n<!-- Add \"scoped\" attribute to limit CSS to this component only -->\r\n<style scoped>\r\n\r\n.grid-container {\r\n  display: grid;\r\n  grid-template-columns: calc(40% - 50px) calc(60% - 50px) 100px;\r\n  padding-bottom: 15px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n.grid-item:not(:last-of-type) {\r\n  padding-right: 10px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n.homey-form-group {\r\n  margin: 0 !important;\r\n}\r\n\r\n.homey-form-label {\r\n  margin-top: 5px !important;\r\n}\r\n\r\n.homey-button-danger-shadow {\r\n  margin-top: 23px;\r\n}\r\n</style>\r\n"],"mappings":"AA+BA,SAASA,UAAU,EAAEC,QAAO,QAAS,OAAM;AAC3C,SAASC,cAAa,QAAS,iBAAgB;AAE/C,eAAe;EACbC,IAAI,EAAE,sBAAsB;EAC5BC,IAAGA,CAAA,EAAK;IACN,OAAO,CAAC;EACV,CAAC;EACDC,QAAQ,EAAE;IACR;IACA,GAAGJ,QAAQ,CAACC,cAAc,EAAE,CAAC,MAAM